Edited [`content/papers/ccarnot.md`](/home/dave/Projects/jaynes-archive/content/papers/ccarnot.md) with structural-only QA changes.

Summary of changes:
- Added/normalized display equation tags so all in-text numeric references resolve (now includes visible tags for `(1)` through `(30)` where referenced, plus existing `(A1)` and `(B1)`).
- Fixed two in-text references from `(2)` to `(2a)` to match the existing referenced equation label.
- Improved markdown readability around many equations by separating prose/equations with blank lines for cleaner Hugo+KaTeX rendering.
- Added missing blank lines before section headings for consistent paragraph/section boundaries.
- Normalized three inline author-year citations to footnote citations and added corresponding footnote definitions:
  - `[^reinhard1950]`
  - `[^gillispie1971]`
  - `[^jaynes1980]`

Self-check completed:
- Intended paragraph/section breaks use blank-line separation.
- No unresolved in-text numeric equation references remain.
